<br>
Regarding bards, don't even bother unless they actually want to fight (which it seems they don't).  They can break a root/snare (including poison) with a single note of their song, which I consider extremely unfair, and will usually just run around so you can't hit them while they sing annoying little "scratch" songs.  Scratch songs being little tunes that hurt like the scratch of a kitten but build up over time.  <br>
